<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc081dc72-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s19156"><num value="19156">§ 19156.</num><heading> Existing activities</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">A Federal research agency may satisfy requirements under this part through activities and programs in existence as of <date date="2022-08-09">August 9, 2022</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc081dc73-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/117/167/dB/tV/s10506">Pub. L. 117–167, div. B, title V, § 10506</ref>, <date date="2022-08-09">Aug. 9, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/1612">136 Stat. 1612</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
